author: dkulp
msg: Update WSDLManager to allow adding wsdls, fix minor issues, enhance WSDLOperationInfo
* Add a addDefinition method to WSDLMananger to allow external application to add parsed wsdls to the celtix cache.
* Update HTTPClientTransport to work if jaxws doesn't set the PortConfiguration. (uses defaults)
* Add some more query methods to the WSDLOperationInfo

author: dkulp
msg: Add initial support for jwsdl based DataBindingCallback information
* Remove some unused methods from the DataBindingCallback interface

* Create base infrustructure for supporting data bindings that are not jax-ws annotation based.   Information is pulled from the wsdl document and cached.   Creating a data binding for a non-jax-ws-annotation based system just will involve the readers/writers if the info is in the wsdl.  (Note: does not support wrapped doc/literal yet)
* Update eclipse warning levels to allow a concrete class to implement an annotation interface.

author: eamdwyer-iona
msg: Changing tests to ensure the same TCP/IP ports are not reused, problems can sporadically occur if port goes into TIME_WAIT status before being reused.

author: eamdwyer-iona
msg: To get more tracing from cruise control, test works fine in local repository
